Minimum Viable Product

Exchange app

Pitch/Idea: users can post items they have laying around the house they no longer need.
users can also see other items posted and get in contact with the owner to work out a deal.


- allow a user to create a account
- let user post an item they want to sell
- create a list of all the items that are for sell
- view an item( title, image, price, description)
- allow a user to favorite an item
- sort item by favorites
- contact another user to purchase an item
